Those charges have been upgraded and he will now appear on Monday in the Mackay Magistrates Court charged with murder.

The elderly man was initially treated in the Mackay Base Hospital for severe injuries to his face and head before being flown to Townsville Hospital.

Police have appealed for witnesses to the incident to contact authorities.

Anyone with information relating to the incident or anyone who may have seen the vehicle have been asked to contact Crime Stoppers on 1800 333 000.

